Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你傷成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.93,0:00:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天看起來也很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種話可以先透過我轉告給她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有點太莫名其妙喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天殲滅魔獸時有點搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本以為只有一隻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果突然分裂成三隻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾會碰上那種魔獸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不要動喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上天之光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以吾之名實現祈求
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.15,0:00:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請治癒負傷之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癒光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好厲害啊 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你會用魔法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就只會用這一種而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:01:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你年紀這麼小就會使用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是魔人族呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾也會使用魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒文語是魔人族的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是凡人族
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有適性是無法發音的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我算是擁有適性的少數派
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇見拉提娜的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以多少有辦法溝通
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是因為我會咒文語的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不會講魔人族的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.51,0:01:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒辦法使用魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡人族雖然也擁有魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.03,0:01:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒有辦法自由駕馭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要使用魔道具
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱水或是火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜在來到庫羅茲之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒有看過魔道具
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔道具是凡人族的特產品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟魔人族跟我們之間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎沒有交流
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼魔人族
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不跟其他人和睦相處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:01:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊 到底為甚麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想學學其他魔法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜想要學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬於冥的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以吾之名實現祈求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪去熱量 讓溫度下降
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫度輕減
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(眼眸的深處照映著我的模樣)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(你的笑容令我感到些許耀眼)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(在四目相對的瞬間)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(便已感受到 I feel it)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(如空中出現的 (那片天空的))
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(那道彩虹一樣 (彩虹一般))
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(閃耀著七色光輝)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(與你共度的時光)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(使我的內心雀躍不已)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(I'm with you)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(不論是笑容 又或是傷悲)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我願分享我的一切)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(只要你能對我微笑)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(哪怕猛烈強風 亦或漫長黑夜)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(只要你陪伴在我身邊 僅僅如此)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(就令我感覺能再踏出下一步)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(為了女兒，我說不定連魔王都能幹掉)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(小小女孩遭遇那件事件)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要離開我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一定會覺得很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:04:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你要忍耐喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是不想和她分開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這也是為了拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是身為監護人的試煉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我克服這道難關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不過是要去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太小題大作了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是我們就讀的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿司法爾的神殿喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都是不認識的小孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也不是只有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這些東區的小孩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來兩年要被逼讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才第一天你在說甚麼傻話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克蘿伊 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨 馬賽爾 安東尼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算我拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別丟我們東區的臉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯迪 早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 你一個人過來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跟克羅伊來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們約好要一起過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜來到庫羅茲也還沒過多久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是魔人族吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才不經意注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用緞帶藏起來的角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是希爾維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從西區過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣叫你沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教 希爾維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次能讓我看看你的角嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也該適可而止了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為甚麼要生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還為甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家回位子上坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一會兒見囉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒見 希爾維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子搞甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西區啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是有錢人家的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿司法爾是司掌學問之神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位同學在神的御名之下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要學習正確的知識才對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是身為人應有的生存之道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是拉提娜做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜在想能不能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用迪爾教的魔法來做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的好厲害啊 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩得很開心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還交到了新的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 還學到了很多新的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:06:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜想學會更多各式各樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.85,0:07:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜果然是個好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別呆在那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼魯迪總是要抓拉提娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.27,0:07:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫拉提娜這麼小又跑得很慢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜才沒有慢吞吞的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為魯迪每次都會先追拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會這樣說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒這回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當事人自己沒察覺這樣正常嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為魯迪還是個小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要上課囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老師動不動就生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話每次都很尖銳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說她是去年新任職的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:07:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很怕她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜也有點怕她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閱讀書籍在日常生活中不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也因此…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔人族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼你這種可恨的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會出現在人類的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這種異形
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能以同樣的樣貌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活過百年以上歲月的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會是人類呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了凡人族以外的亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是像這樣擁有異形象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連生命本身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不同於人類的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不能被他們騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是魔人族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都是與魔王掛勾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行邪惡之事的卑劣生物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可對他們大意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像她這樣隱藏自己的身分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混入人群之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是最好的鐵證
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.78,0:09:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克蘿伊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克蘿伊‧施奈德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.46,0:09:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我停手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽敢對神官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出這種大不敬行為之人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會立刻將他們逐出校門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就把我們趕出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾維亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦被逐出校門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你的家人也會因此蒙羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道別人家是怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想我父親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會稱讚我做得好才對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我告訴他有個會把學生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說成是怪物的老師的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我停手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我停手 給我停手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通通給我安靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要將魔人族排除殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是令人厭惡的種族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 到底有甚麼不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔人族跟大家有甚麼不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命本身不同是甚麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能活上百年是甚麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大家都不一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡人族跟魔人族最大的差異
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是外表上的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔人族是能比凡人族多活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超過一倍以上歲月的種族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生甚麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.65,0:11:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.25,0:11:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水結冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要將魔力集中在一個點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能發揮出超出原本的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾說他今天會晚一點才回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎 肯尼斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們之中有誰會用回復魔法的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的魔法能做的事情有限喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先快點幫她止血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼斯 拉提娜她怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之現在要先幫她做治療
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要帶她到尼利神殿的治療院去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾回來後幫我轉告他一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.73,0:12:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天先關店了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼斯 拉提娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的性命似乎沒有大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼要把自己的角…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向她問清這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是迪爾你的責任了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉塔跟常客們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在肯定擔心到不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼斯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為甚麼要這樣做…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.49,0:13:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜不需要甚麼魔人族的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是拉提娜沒有甚麼角就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生甚麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…為甚麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼拉提娜是魔人族
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜明明就不住在魔人族的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔人族明明就不要拉提娜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會關心拉提娜的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說拉提娜可以待在這裡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是街上的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有拉提娜的時間跟大家不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大家死掉以後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有拉提娜會被獨自留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不想再孤獨一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不想再只有拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人被留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜想跟迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有大家永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不想再孤單一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算拉提娜同樣也是凡人族
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會比拉提娜先一步死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的年紀比你大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我做的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可能會喪命的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽我說 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很慶幸能夠跟你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很慶幸能在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有限的時間之中和你一起度過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很慶幸能和拉提娜相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.89,0:15:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事我絕對不會感到後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說我希望拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也別說甚麼如果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒遇見我就好了之類的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很慶幸可以遇見迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很慶幸能和拉提娜相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算死亡到來的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一定能夠這樣斷言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在那一天到來前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要一直在一起喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜很慶幸能遇見迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜也最最喜歡迪爾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身為擁有高階神官位之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於我為甚麼會來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該也沒必要再多做說明了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從孩子們口中聽說事情的經過了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說她在那些孩子面前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侮辱魔人族這個種族
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還沒來由地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口出惡言 高談闊論呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡人族至上主義者並不稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有要否定的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然生活在這與許多旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有密切關係的城鎮中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這實在是一種相當狹隘的見解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…擔任教師的那位神官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親人在與魔人族的爭執中喪命了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是因為這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能將毫無罪孽的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斥為怪物並汙辱她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 絕對沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說她以前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾引發過類似的事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她才會被人連忙調到庫羅茲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為甚麼會知道這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你應該也很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我身邊有蒐集情報的專家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我也有向他們請求情報的權利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要根據我的加護
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求行使裁定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.11,0:17:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.36,0:17:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們還打算繼續包庇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出那種事的卑劣之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必你們也做好相對的覺悟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的覺悟是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要透過阿夫馬爾的神殿提出申訴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你所知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭之神阿夫馬爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時也是司掌調停與制裁之神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡將會下達無比殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻又適切的制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦這一連串的事情曝光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想默許這一切的你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屆時恐怕也會被問罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會解除她的職務
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時剝奪她身為神官的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這其實是我在遷怒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼魔人族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不跟其他人和睦相處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時要是能不逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將理由好好說清楚的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我沒教導她攻擊魔法的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜就不會將自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷成那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克蘿伊過來探望她了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的角明明那麼漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有沒有那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜都是拉提娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然做那種死掉也不奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 克蘿伊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然已經鬧成一片了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明連主角都還未登場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們下去吧 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉古死掉的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜以為自己也要死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾找到了拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說拉提娜可以一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜覺得好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉塔跟肯尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有客人們都好溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還遇見了克蘿伊她們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.89,0:19:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為每天都過得好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜都差點忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡跟分離都是遲早會到來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜希望能一直這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才開始變得害怕分離
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都會害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我聽說拉提娜受重傷時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都以為心臟要停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克蘿伊她也哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不希望和拉提娜分開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜覺得好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜很慶幸能來到庫羅茲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很慶幸能遇見大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜現在能這麼幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是因為迪爾找到了拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看板娘回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主角登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是慶祝拉提娜痊癒的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請你們所有人都喝一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太小氣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該要全額買單才像是個男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們一定會喝到我破產為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉塔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這間店裡最好的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給每個人都來一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有珍藏的上等好酒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會難得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用店裡最大的酒杯來倒酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:20:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下 肯尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:21:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種酒正常不會用啤酒杯倒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說甚麼傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.91,0:21:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆說沒問題就沒問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這對夫婦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起讓大家擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜已經打起精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後也會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.22,0:21:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是了漂亮的開場白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在無法想像她才八歲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的拉提娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她既可愛又靈巧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還很懂事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是完美無缺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 機會難得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們聽你獻唱一曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獻唱一曲是甚麼意思 瑟德利克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.94,0:21:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要你唱唱歌的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.63,0:21:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒聽過拉提娜唱歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜要唱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:22:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽升起了 鳥兒齊歌唱…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.72,0:22:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子果然還是要有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅長的事情才比較可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.24,0:22:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(每過一秒 對你的喜歡就增加一點)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(當你磨蹭我的臉龐 一切都變得不再重要)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.88,0:22:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(發生在世上的紛爭 都敵不過這個瞬間)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(如果可以真希望明天或者後天)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.72,0:22:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(都因為溺愛中毒丟下工作不管)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(已經超乎保護過度 愛操心的毛病)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.46,0:22:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(使得我變得異常堅強)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.05,0:22:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我已下定決心要守護你)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(只要是為了你的笑容)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.97,0:23:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我甚至能與正義為敵)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.16,0:23:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(This is 勇者 but 殘念!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.15,0:23:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(對你深深著迷)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.90,0:23:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(甜甜蜜蜜或是卿卿我我)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.49,0:23:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(都是傻爸爸的末期症狀)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.45,0:23:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(只要有你在 就算當個殘念勇者也無所謂)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.83,0:23:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(所以請你永遠陪伴在我身邊)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(到連冒險也無法繼續的地步)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(This is 勇者 but 殘念)